  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Aweil and Yirol: Piloting DAP Technology on Action Plan for Peace and Gender based violent project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Baseline Survey in Aweil and Yirol
- Purchase of Digital Audio Player (DAP)
- Writing and recording of Scripts on Peace Building and Gender Based Violence
- Boosting, Conversion and downloading of messages in to DAPs
- Community Mobilization (Formation of listening groups)
- Development of M&amp;E tool</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">- Enhanced CA/CTP/SSCC understanding and evidence on how ICCs could be strengthened to implement the APP at local level, to inform future programming
- Hard to reach communities are engaged through use of innovative technology</narrative>
  </description>
